Dear fellow dumbs,

This tutorial is written from my newbie experience, setting up haraka. I hope this could save your valuable time.

What we will do
1. Install haraka
2. Setup initial configuration and test
3. Config password authentication for outbound (sending email to another domain) and test
4. Config TLS encryption (so haraka will accept the email sent from email client e.g. outlook, thunderbird)

What you need before getting start
1. You can use unix-like commandline. (e.g. OSX terminal)
2. You know what 'sudo' command is.
3. You have NodeJS installed.
4. You know what dependencies are and know how to fix them.

Install Haraka

sudo npm -g install Haraka

this will setup haraka in your OS. As the result, 
